Comment.val: /* Program to obtain the data for the custodian after the split batchopdrachten (procesid=11004) have finished */.

/* The following numbers can be used: 1 = Check if the number of securities depository is 1, if not, the sort will be changed 2 = Get the totals of the taxes en the corresponding componentcodes to use in de custodian transaction */

Text.val: 1 = Controleren aantal bewaarplaatsen en aanpassen sortering
2 = Totalen belasting en de componentcodes voor de belastingen ophalen

SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from ca_werkbestand c where c.cawb_terminalnummer = ~1 and c.cawb_sortering = ~2
update ca_werkbestand set cawb_sortering = ~1 where cawb_terminalnummer = ~2 and cawb_sortering = ~3
select c.cawb_symbool, sum(c.cawb_wht), sum(c.cawb_rv) from ca_werkbestand c where c.cawb_terminalnummer = ~1 and c.cawb_sortering = ~2 group by c.cawb_symbool

select sum(A.wbkl_saldopositie),sum(A.wbkl_aantal_effbedrag), sum(round(A.wbkl_aantal_effbedrag,~3)) from werkbestand_kalenderacties A where A.wbkl_kalendersoort=~1 and A.wbkl_terminalnummer=~2 and A.wbkl_sortering <> 2
